org.jasig.cas.support.saml.authentication.principal

Class SamlService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.authentication.principal.AbstractWebApplicationService
      • org.jasig.cas.support.saml.authentication.principal.SamlService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Principal, Service, SingleLogoutService, WebApplicationService

    public final class SamlService
extends AbstractWebApplicationService
    Class to represent that this service wants to use SAML. We use this in combination with the CentralAuthenticationServiceImpl to choose the right UniqueTicketIdGenerator.
    Since:
    3.1
    Author:
    Scott Battaglia
